data.description: Charming 3 bed, 2.5 bath home in Tuscumbia, AL. Enjoy a spacious kitchen with island, large great room with gas fireplace, and formal dining area. New front windows (2023), 2 HVAC units replaced (2022/2023), and a generous pantry. 2-car garage. Less than 5 mins from Muscle Shoals center. Perfect blend of comfort and convenience! All information is to be verified by the purchaser.
